《'''致命武器'''》（{{lang-en|''Lethal Weapon''}}）是一部於[[福斯廣播公司|Fox]]播出的美國電視劇，改編自[[沙恩·布萊克|沙恩·布萊克]]的[[致命武器|同名]]系列電影。該劇於2016年9月21日首播<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/05/the-exorcist-lethal-weapon-making-history-pitch-the-mick-apb-fox-series-orders-1201752948/|title=‘The Exorcist’, ‘Lethal Weapon’, ‘Making History’, ‘Pitch’, ‘The Mick’ & ‘APB’ Get Fox Series Orders|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|accessdate=2016-05-11|date=2016-05-10|first=Nellie|last=Andreeva|publisher=[[Penske_Media_Corporation|Penske Media Corporation]]|location=United States|archive-date=2017-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170802092034/http://deadline.com/2016/05/the-exorcist-lethal-weapon-making-history-pitch-the-mick-apb-fox-series-orders-1201752948/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年10月12日，Fox宣布預訂全季集數18集<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/10/lethal-weapon-order-five-episodes-season-1-fox-full-season-1201835268/|title=‘Lethal Weapon’ Gets Order For 5 More Episodes In Season 1 From Fox|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2016-10-12|accessdate=2016-10-12|archive-date=2018-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180628205033/https://deadline.com/2016/10/lethal-weapon-order-five-episodes-season-1-fox-full-season-1201835268/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年2月22日，Fox續訂該劇的第二季<ref name="#1">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/02/lethal-weapon-renewed-season-2-fox-1201940952/|title=‘Lethal Weapon’ Renewed For Season 2 By Fox|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2017-02-22|accessdate=2017-02-22|archive-date=2017-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222223352/http://deadline.com/2017/02/lethal-weapon-renewed-season-2-fox-1201940952/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第二季定於2017年9月26日起播出，共22集<ref name="#1"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2017/tv/news/fox-fall-premiere-dates-1202475957/|title=Fox Sets Fall Premiere Dates, Including 'Empire,' 'The Gifted,' 'The Orville'|work=Variety|last=Holloway|first=Daniel|date=2017-06-22|accessdate=2017-06-22|archive-date=2017-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170622201203/http://variety.com/2017/tv/news/fox-fall-premiere-dates-1202475957/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Season2-22>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/lethal-weapon-renewed-season-2-978484|title=Fox's 'Lethal Weapon' Renewed for Season 2|work=Hollywood Reporter|last=Stanhope|first=Kate|date=2017-02-22|accessdate=2018-02-28|archive-date=2018-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180301044438/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/lethal-weapon-renewed-season-2-978484|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

第二季播出中期，由於主演之一的[[克雷恩·柯洛佛|克雷恩·柯洛佛]]被指控行為不當（多次與劇組及演員們產生對立）而在該季播畢後，他便被Fox開除。2018年5月13日，Fox續訂第三季，且由[[西恩·威廉·史考特|西恩·威廉·史考特]]飾演一名新角色，以來取代柯洛佛擔任主角<ref name="SeannWilliamScott">{{cite news|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/tv/2018/05/13/lethal-weapon-renewed-fox-new-co-star-seann-william-scott/605960002/|title='Lethal Weapon' renewed, but Seann William Scott replaces fired star Clayne Crawford|last=Levin|first=Gary|work=USA TODAY|date=2018-05-13|accessdate=2018-05-14|archive-date=2018-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180514025215/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/tv/2018/05/13/lethal-weapon-renewed-fox-new-co-star-seann-william-scott/605960002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第三季於2018年9月25日起播出，共15集。

2019年5月10日，該劇被Fox宣布取消<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/05/lethal-weapon-canceled-fox-three-seasons-1202605535/|title=‘Lethal Weapon’ Canceled By Fox After 3 Seasons|last=Andreeva|first=Nellie|work=Deadline Hollywood|date=2019-05-10|accessdate=2019-05-10|archive-date=2019-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190510195651/https://deadline.com/2019/05/lethal-weapon-canceled-fox-three-seasons-1202605535/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 劇情 ==
故事敘述[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]是座犯罪率相當高的城市，{{le|羅傑·墨陶|Roger Murtaugh}}和{{le|馬丁·瑞格|Martin Riggs}}是洛杉磯警局中的警探搭檔，兩人必須聯手共同解決城市中發生的各種大小犯罪事件，但也因此惹出一連串的麻煩。

